<ul>
  <li>Use APP to Turn on the Flashlight</li>
  <li>Flip your Camera to Show <%= booking.user %> your Problem.</li>
  <li>Use Red Button to End Video Chat</li>
</ul>
<br/>
<b>Note:</b>
<ul>
  <li>In case you are unable to call, your amount will be refunded in you account within 6-7 working days.</li>
</ul>

<br/>
